data.description: This lovely home sits on 6.26 acres!  It has been very well maintained and occupied by its original owners who had the home built from the ground up.  There are 4 nice sized bedrooms PLUS a bonus room.  Three of the 4 bedrooms have walk-in closets!  The home is energy efficient, double insulated, and even has a water manifold.  The beautiful grounds of the property consists of a fully fenced acre in the front yard, Pecan trees, Blueberry bushes, Hazelnut bushes, Mature Trees (Oaks, Pines, and Cedars) along with a very long driveway from the main road back to the crush & run driveway that leads to the home.  Park your cars under the double carport and enjoy a cup of coffee or a nice sunset on the small paver patio in the front yard.  There are 2 storage buildings (12x24 & 12x10) that also come with the property.  Make this beautiful home your own, call today to schedule your tour!
